BUILDING AND RUNNING A QT EMULATOR

BUILDING:

All platforms:

In the android/skin/qt directory,

    find . | grep Makefile | xargs rm
    /path/to/Qt/5.4/<qt-architecture>/bin/qmake
    make

In Makefile.common,

    EMULATOR_USE_QT ?= true
    EMULATOR_USE_SDL2 ?= false

    adjust QT_HOME

In android/config.h:

    //#define CONFIG_SDL 0
    #define CONFIG_QT 1

On your platform, you may need to set LD_LIBRARY_PATH or DYLD_LIBRARY_PATH to point to the Qt libs and/or platform directories.
